      <title>配置记录</title>
      <link href="/2021/09/23/pei-zhi-ji-lu/"/>
      <url>/2021/09/23/pei-zhi-ji-lu/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>[TOC]</p><h2 id="任务列表"><a href="#任务列表" class="headerlink" title="任务列表"></a>任务列表</h2><ul><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox">  文章加密</p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox">  评论模块</p></li></ul><h2 id="2021-9-24"><a href="#2021-9-24" class="headerlink" title="2021/9/24"></a>2021/9/24</h2><h2 id="2021-9-23"><a href="#2021-9-23" class="headerlink" title="2021/9/23"></a>2021/9/23</h2><ul><li>配置per_page为12</li><li>添加搜索功能</li><li>添加代码高亮</li><li>添加代码可复制</li></ul><h2 id="2021-9-22及以前"><a href="#2021-9-22及以前" class="headerlink" title="2021/9/22及以前"></a>2021/9/22及以前</h2><ul><li>添加live2d</li><li>修改网站LOGO、主题等相关信息</li><li>添加加载动画</li><li>….</li></ul><h2 id="配置相关问题"><a href="#配置相关问题" class="headerlink" title="配置相关问题"></a>配置相关问题</h2><h3 id="一、提交问题"><a href="#一、提交问题" class="headerlink" title="一、提交问题"></a>一、提交问题</h3><p>​    有时候提交会报错：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">fatal: unable to access <span class="token string">'https://github.com/xxx/autowrite.git/'</span><span class="token builtin class-name">:</span> OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno <span class="token number">10054</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>又或</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">fatal: unable to access <span class="token string">'https://github.com/xxx/autowrite.git/'</span><span class="token builtin class-name">:</span>Failed to connect to github.com port <span class="token number">443</span>: Timed out<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>问题分析：</strong></p><p>git在拉取或者提交项目时，中间会有git的http和https代理，但是我们本地环境本身就有SSL协议了，所以取消git的https代理即可，不行再取消http的代理。</p><p>另一个原因就是当前的代理网速太慢了，会出现偶尔成功，偶尔失败的情况</p><p><strong>解决方案：</strong></p><ol><li><p>在项目文件夹的命令行窗口执行下面代码</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">//取消https代理 <span class="token function">git</span> config --global --unset https.proxy//取消http代理<span class="token function">git</span> config --global --unset http.proxy<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>然后再git commit或git clone</p></li><li><p>科学上网</p><p>提高服务器连接速度，能从根本解决 time out 443问题</p></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
